任天堂博物馆的正式名称（暂定名）已确定为“任天堂博物馆” https://p2y.jp/nintendo-resource-center-officially-name-nintendo-museum/ https://p2y.jp/nintendo-resource-center-officially-name-nintendo-museum/#respondp2y_admin Thu, 14 Sep 2023 14:54:23 +0000 ゲーム任天堂Nintendo DirectTwitterYouTubeニンテンドーミュージアム(Nintendo MUSEUM) https://p2y.jp/?p=101102 <p>在 2023 年 9 月 14 日的 Nintendo Direct 直播中，任天堂宣布将展示该公司过去发布的产品的任天堂博物馆（暂定名）的正式名称更改为“Ninten […]</p>该帖子<a href="https://p2y.jp/nintendo-resource-center-officially-name-nintendo-museum/">任天堂博物馆的正式名称（暂定名称）已确定为“Nintendo Museum”，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p> 2023年9月14日（令和5年）任天堂直播期间，任天堂宣布将展示该公司过去发布的产品的任天堂博物馆（暂定名）的正式名称改为<strong>任天堂博物馆</strong>。已经决定了。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-attachment-id="101108" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/nintendo-resource-center-officially-name-nintendo-museum/nintendo_museum_image/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nintendo_museum_image.png" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="nintendo_museum_image" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nintendo_museum_image.png" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nintendo_museum_image.png" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="675" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nintendo_museum_image.png" alt="任天堂博物馆的正式名称（暂定名）已确定为“任天堂博物馆”" class="wp-image-101108"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：X（推特）<br> ©任天堂</figcaption></figure><figure class="wp-block-image"><img data-attachment-id="41957" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/nintendo_renovates_uji_ogura_plant_as_nintendo_museum/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/nintendo_renovates_uji_ogura_plant_as_nintendo_museum.jpg" data-orig-size="1024,578" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="nintendo_renovates_uji_ogura_plant_as_nintendo_museum" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/nintendo_renovates_uji_ogura_plant_as_nintendo_museum.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/nintendo_renovates_uji_ogura_plant_as_nintendo_museum.jpg" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1024" height="578" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/nintendo_renovates_uji_ogura_plant_as_nintendo_museum.jpg" alt="任天堂宇治小仓工厂将改建为“任天堂博物馆（暂名）” 预计2023年竣工" class="wp-image-41957"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿©任天堂</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>“任天堂博物馆”是利用该公司宇治小仓工厂的场地和建筑作为服务中心的旅游设施，该工厂主要生产扑克牌和花札以及修理游戏机作为服务中心。目前正在建设中，目标是在财政年度内完成截至 2024 年 3 月的年度。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="任天堂直面会 2023.9.14" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6GtVjxdKM04?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><div class="kskwd6505b74ddf7ab" ><script async src="https://pagead2.